♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

583
00:35:57,580 --> 00:36:00,800
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

584
00:36:00,830 --> 00:36:05,290
♪ To make it come true ♪

585
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:21,110
[Spirit Tablet of Duan Ying, Late Husband
of the White Horse Battalion, Beifu Army]

586
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:35,780
[To Mother, Respectfully from
Your Son Xiao Wuyi]

587
00:36:52,930 --> 00:36:56,030
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

588
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:06,880
His Majesty says you are a hero to Ye,

589
00:37:07,670 --> 00:37:10,840
and a benefactor to the people
of the three northern prefectures.

590
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,570
You can have whatever you want.

591
00:37:17,590 --> 00:37:20,390
Young Lord Xiao,
the imperial doctor has arrived.

592
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,620
I'm fine. I'm very...

593
00:37:24,120 --> 00:37:24,670
Yao.

594
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:27,530
Yao, stop talking
if you want to recover quickly.

595
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,110
Don't be mad.

596
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:34,400
Please apply the medicine
and acupuncture to Yao immediately.

597
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:35,150
-Yes.
-Yes.

598
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:38,920
Tell Mother

599
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:40,420
not to blame Wuyi.

600
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,560
I'm very happy today.

601
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,330
What did the doctor say?

602
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:50,400
He is very strong.

603
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,880
He endured the pain

604
00:37:52,380 --> 00:37:54,900
and refused to show it in front of us.

605
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:59,440
But all his internal organs are injured.

606
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:01,890
He'll need to rest well for a while.

607
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,670
It's my fault for returning too late.

608
00:38:04,670 --> 00:38:06,030
You don't need to blame yourself.

609
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,360
Yao is very happy today.

610
00:38:07,510 --> 00:38:09,840
At least he proved to everyone

611
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,480
that the Prince Jing'an's Mansion

612
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:14,610
is not represented by Xiao Wuyi alone.

613
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,070
Mother.

614
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:53,190
I...

615
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,190
Let me see.

616
00:39:08,630 --> 00:39:09,360
Does it hurt?

617
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,070
Jiayu said

618
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:16,670
a child who doesn't cry out in pain
isn't necessarily pain-free.

619
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:39,360
Yaoyao,

620
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,440
what is that?

621
00:39:43,670 --> 00:39:46,230
I've been learning lightness skills
from Yan Yue lately.

622
00:39:46,230 --> 00:39:48,070
Every morning I wear these sandbags

623
00:39:48,070 --> 00:39:50,000
to train at the martial arts arena.

624
00:39:50,590 --> 00:39:52,250
But you used to be the laziest,

625
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,880
and you hated getting hurt.

626
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:55,540
It's all because of Xiao Wuyi.

627
00:39:55,730 --> 00:39:57,590
Last time he left me stranded
at the Honglu Temple.

628
00:39:57,590 --> 00:39:59,650
It took me a whole night to climb down.

629
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:03,310
But he was right about one thing.

630
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:04,670
If you want to play with fire,

631
00:40:04,670 --> 00:40:06,230
you have to learn how to escape first.

632
00:40:06,230 --> 00:40:07,880
Since I want to travel the world,

633
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,080
I not only need money,

634
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:11,760
but also some martial arts
to protect myself.

635
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:15,360
Silly.

636
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,250
I will protect you.

637
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:19,000
You don't need to learn these things.

638
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,530
And I won't let you get hurt.

639
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:21,680
How could that work?

640
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:23,670
I have to rely on myself
when I'm away from home.

641
00:40:23,670 --> 00:40:25,670
How can I rely on you for everything?

642
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,060
Today, you and Wuyi

643
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:30,890
worked really well together.

644
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:33,400
I didn't expect you to learn
how to use war drums.

645
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,360
You gave him that sleeve arrow too, right?

646
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:36,590
Yes. How was it?

647
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:38,050
Didn't I look impressive?

648
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:40,820
Not to mention my excellent craftsmanship.

649
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,680
Today was so satisfying.

650
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,760
But you always used to say

651
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,550
that battlefields are lawless,

652
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,840
and that you hated killing the most.

653
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:51,840
Isn't peace the most important thing?

654
00:40:51,840 --> 00:40:53,510
But the Eagle King brought the fight
to our doorstep.

655
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:54,920
How could I tolerate that?

656
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:56,670
Besides, the day the Eagle King
entered the city,

657
00:40:56,670 --> 00:40:59,130
weren't you and the students
indignant too?

658
00:40:59,300 --> 00:41:00,480
Fortunately, today,

659
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:02,280
Xiao Wuyi rooted out
the Northern Qin spies,

660
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,800
reclaimed the three prefectures,

661
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,000
and vented our anger.

662
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:08,630
Sometimes fists really are the only truth.

663
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,530
That saying is really true.

664
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:13,110
I even designed a sword for Xiao Wuyi,

665
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:15,630
one no less impressive
than the Longque Blade.

666
00:41:15,630 --> 00:41:16,550
A man like him

667
00:41:17,110 --> 00:41:19,170
deserves the best sword in the world.

668
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:21,550
But don't you feel

669
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,320
today all of us

670
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,440
were used by Wuyi?

671
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:27,360
In this battle, he not only won back
the three prefectures,

672
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,960
but the prestige
he gained from turning the tide

673
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:31,800
also laid the foundation for his future reform
of the Northern Prefecture.

674
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:33,440
He was the one who sought peace talks,

675
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:35,900
and he is the one
who won the people's hearts.

676
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:39,000
But is there anything wrong with that?

677
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:41,600
A person with the ability
and will to protect Ye

678
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:43,200
deserves such prestige.

679
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:46,110
I thought

680
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:49,230
you liked people
who stay aloof from the world.

681
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:52,550
I do like staying aloof from the world,

682
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,030
but I can choose not to fight

683
00:41:54,030 --> 00:41:56,490
because someone
is already fighting for me.

684
00:41:59,590 --> 00:42:00,480
Then what if

685
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,760
I want to fight too?

